flowchart TD
    Start([Caller holds SOS button]) --> DetectLoc[App detects GPS location]
    DetectLoc --> ConfirmLoc{Caller confirms<br/>or adjusts pin on map?}
    ConfirmLoc -->|Adjust| DragPin[Drag pin / tap map<br/>to correct location]
    DragPin --> ConfirmLoc
    ConfirmLoc -->|Confirm| AddDetails[Optionally add address<br/>note / description]
    AddDetails --> Validate{Backend validates<br/>request data}
    Validate -->|Invalid| ShowError[Show error,<br/>caller corrects and resubmits]
    ShowError --> AddDetails
    Validate -->|Valid| GenID[Generate unique emergency ID]
    GenID --> FindNearest[Compute nearest hospital<br/>to confirmed location]
    FindNearest --> SaveCall[Save emergency call,<br/>status = pending,<br/>emergency_type = medical,<br/>assigned_hospital_id = nearest]
    SaveCall --> ShowID[Display emergency ID<br/>to caller]
    ShowID --> StreamLoc[Caller device streams<br/>live location continuously]

    StreamLoc --> DispatcherView[Only the assigned hospital's<br/>dispatcher sees the call<br/>in their active queue, sorted by severity]
    DispatcherView --> SelectCall[Dispatcher selects the call]
    SelectCall --> ViewMap[Dispatcher views caller's<br/>live location on map]
    ViewMap --> CheckCrew{Is a crewed ambulance<br/>available?}
    CheckCrew -->|No| AssignDriver[Dispatcher assigns a driver<br/>to an ambulance on Crew screen]
    AssignDriver --> CheckCrew
    CheckCrew -->|Yes| SelectAmb[Dispatcher picks ambulance<br/>from nearest-first list]
    SelectAmb --> SelectHospital[Dispatcher optionally picks<br/>destination hospital,<br/>nearest-first list]
    SelectHospital --> CreateDispatch[Create dispatch record]
    CreateDispatch --> StatusAssigned[Call status to assigned,<br/>ambulance status to dispatched]

    StatusAssigned --> DriverNotified[Driver sees active dispatch]
    DriverNotified --> ViewCallerLoc[Driver views caller's<br/>live location on map]
    ViewCallerLoc --> TapOnWay[Driver taps<br/>'On the way']
    TapOnWay --> StatusEnRoute[Call status to en_route,<br/>ambulance status to en_route]
    StatusEnRoute --> GPSStream[Ambulance streams<br/>live GPS to backend]
    GPSStream --> TapArrived[Driver taps<br/>'Arrived at scene']
    TapArrived --> StatusOnScene[Call status to on_scene]
    StatusOnScene --> TapDeparting[Driver taps<br/>'Departing scene']
    TapDeparting --> StatusTransporting[Call status to transporting]
    StatusTransporting --> TapHospital[Driver taps<br/>'Arrived at hospital']
    TapHospital --> StatusCompleted[Call status to completed,<br/>ambulance status to available]

    StatusCompleted --> CallerSees[Caller's tracking screen<br/>shows 'Help has arrived']
    CallerSees --> AdminRecord[Call and full status timeline<br/>available in admin system records]
    AdminRecord --> End([End])

    SaveCall -.->|Caller may cancel<br/>at any point before completion| Cancelled[Call status to cancelled]
    Cancelled --> End
